{"key":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01|2Th|3","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"2Th","chapter":3,"textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024","parserRevision":"v10","verses":[{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Th:3:1","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"2Th","bookOrder":52,"chapter":3,"verse":1,"text":"In addition, brothers and sisters, pray for us that the word of the Lord may spread rapidly and be honored, just as it was with you,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Th:3:2","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"2Th","bookOrder":52,"chapter":3,"verse":2,"text":"and that we may be delivered from wicked and evil people, for not all have faith.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Th:3:3","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"2Th","bookOrder":52,"chapter":3,"verse":3,"text":"But the Lord is faithful; he will strengthen you and guard you from the evil one.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Th:3:4","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"2Th","bookOrder":52,"chapter":3,"verse":4,"text":"We have confidence in the Lord about you, that you are doing and will continue to do what we command.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Th:3:5","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"2Th","bookOrder":52,"chapter":3,"verse":5,"text":"May the Lord direct your hearts to God’s love and Christ’s endurance.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Th:3:6","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"2Th","bookOrder":52,"chapter":3,"verse":6,"text":"Now we command you, brothers and sisters, in the name of our Lord Jesus Christ, to keep away from every brother or sister who is idle and does not live according to the tradition received from us.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Th:3:7","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"2Th","bookOrder":52,"chapter":3,"verse":7,"text":"For you yourselves know how you should imitate us: We were not idle among you;","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Th:3:8","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"2Th","bookOrder":52,"chapter":3,"verse":8,"text":"we did not eat anyone’s food free of charge; instead, we labored and toiled, working night and day, so that we would not be a burden to any of you.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Th:3:9","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"2Th","bookOrder":52,"chapter":3,"verse":9,"text":"It is not that we don’t have the right to support, but we did it to make ourselves an example to you so that you would imitate us.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Th:3:10","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"2Th","bookOrder":52,"chapter":3,"verse":10,"text":"In fact, when we were with you, this is what we commanded you: “If anyone isn’t willing to work, he should not eat.”","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Th:3:11","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"2Th","bookOrder":52,"chapter":3,"verse":11,"text":"For we hear that there are some among you who are idle. They are not busy but busybodies.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Th:3:12","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"2Th","bookOrder":52,"chapter":3,"verse":12,"text":"Now we command and exhort such people by the Lord Jesus Christ to work quietly and provide for themselves.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Th:3:13","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"2Th","bookOrder":52,"chapter":3,"verse":13,"text":"But as for you, brothers and sisters, do not grow weary in doing good.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Th:3:14","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"2Th","bookOrder":52,"chapter":3,"verse":14,"text":"If anyone does not obey our instruction in this letter, take note of that person; don’t associate with him, so that he may be ashamed.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Th:3:15","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"2Th","bookOrder":52,"chapter":3,"verse":15,"text":"Yet don’t consider him as an enemy, but warn him as a brother.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Th:3:16","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"2Th","bookOrder":52,"chapter":3,"verse":16,"text":"May the Lord of peace himself give you peace always in every way. The Lord be with all of you.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Th:3:17","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"2Th","bookOrder":52,"chapter":3,"verse":17,"text":"I, Paul, am writing this greeting with my own hand, which is an authenticating mark in every letter; this is how I write.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Th:3:18","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"2Th","bookOrder":52,"chapter":3,"verse":18,"text":"The grace of our Lord Jesus Christ be with you all.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"}],"layout":{"bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"2Th","chapter":3,"paragraphStarts":[1,6,14,16],"headings":[{"beforeVerse":1,"text":"Pray for Us"},{"beforeVerse":6,"text":"Warning against Irresponsible Behavior"},{"beforeVerse":16,"text":"Final Greetings"}],"poetryBlocks":[],"studyByVerse":[{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Th:3:1","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"In addition, brothers and sisters, pray for us that the word of the Lord may spread rapidly and be honored, just as it was with you, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Th 2:13","book":"1Th","chapter":2,"verse":13,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"1Th 2:13","book":"1Th","chapter":2,"verse":13}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Th:3:2","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"and that we may be delivered "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 27:43","book":"Mat","chapter":27,"verse":43,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 15:31","book":"Rom","chapter":15,"verse":31,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" from wicked and evil people, for not all have faith. "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Or for the faith is not in everyone"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mt 27:43","book":"Mat","chapter":27,"verse":43},{"label":"Rm 15:31","book":"Rom","chapter":15,"verse":31}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Or for the faith is not in everyone"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Th:3:3","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"But the Lord is faithful; he will strengthen you and guard you from the evil one. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 5:37","book":"Mat","chapter":5,"verse":37,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 6:13","book":"Mat","chapter":6,"verse":13,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 13:19","book":"Mat","chapter":13,"verse":19,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 13:38","book":"Mat","chapter":13,"verse":38,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 17:15","book":"Jhn","chapter":17,"verse":15,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Eph 6:16","book":"Eph","chapter":6,"verse":16,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Jn 2:13–14","book":"1Jn","chapter":2,"verse":13,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Jn 3:12","book":"1Jn","chapter":3,"verse":12,"letter":"h"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Jn 5:18–19","book":"1Jn","chapter":5,"verse":18,"letter":"i"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mt 5:37","book":"Mat","chapter":5,"verse":37},{"label":"Mt 6:13","book":"Mat","chapter":6,"verse":13},{"label":"Mt 13:19","book":"Mat","chapter":13,"verse":19},{"label":"Mt 13:38","book":"Mat","chapter":13,"verse":38},{"label":"Jn 17:15","book":"Jhn","chapter":17,"verse":15},{"label":"Eph 6:16","book":"Eph","chapter":6,"verse":16},{"label":"1Jn 2:13–14","book":"1Jn","chapter":2,"verse":13},{"label":"1Jn 3:12","book":"1Jn","chapter":3,"verse":12},{"label":"1Jn 5:18–19","book":"1Jn","chapter":5,"verse":18}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Th:3:4","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"We have confidence in the Lord about you, that you are doing and will continue to do what we command. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Th:3:5","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"May the Lord direct your hearts to God’s love and Christ’s endurance. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 15:5","book":"Rom","chapter":15,"verse":5,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rv 13:10","book":"Rev","chapter":13,"verse":10,"letter":"b"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Rm 15:5","book":"Rom","chapter":15,"verse":5},{"label":"Rv 13:10","book":"Rev","chapter":13,"verse":10}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Th:3:6","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Now we command you, brothers and sisters, in the name "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 14:13","book":"Jhn","chapter":14,"verse":13,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 3:16","book":"Act","chapter":3,"verse":16,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 15:14","book":"Act","chapter":15,"verse":14,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Php 2:10","book":"Php","chapter":2,"verse":10,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" of our Lord Jesus Christ, to keep away from every brother or sister "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 18:17","book":"Mat","chapter":18,"verse":17,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 5:11","book":"1Co","chapter":5,"verse":11,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Tm 3:5","book":"2Ti","chapter":3,"verse":5,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Jn 10","book":"2Jn","chapter":1,"verse":10,"letter":"h"},{"kind":"text","text":" who is idle and does not live "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Lit walk"},{"kind":"text","text":" according to the tradition "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mk 7:3","book":"Mrk","chapter":7,"verse":3,"letter":"i"},{"kind":"text","text":" received "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jd 1:3","book":"Jud","chapter":1,"verse":3,"letter":"j"},{"kind":"text","text":" from us. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jn 14:13","book":"Jhn","chapter":14,"verse":13},{"label":"Ac 3:16","book":"Act","chapter":3,"verse":16},{"label":"Ac 15:14","book":"Act","chapter":15,"verse":14},{"label":"Php 2:10","book":"Php","chapter":2,"verse":10},{"label":"Mt 18:17","book":"Mat","chapter":18,"verse":17},{"label":"1Co 5:11","book":"1Co","chapter":5,"verse":11},{"label":"2Tm 3:5","book":"2Ti","chapter":3,"verse":5},{"label":"2Jn 10","book":"2Jn","chapter":1,"verse":10},{"label":"Mk 7:3","book":"Mrk","chapter":7,"verse":3},{"label":"Jd 1:3","book":"Jud","chapter":1,"verse":3}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Lit walk"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Th:3:7","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"For you yourselves know how you should imitate "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"3Jn 11","book":"3Jn","chapter":1,"verse":11,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" us: We were not idle among you; "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"3Jn 11","book":"3Jn","chapter":1,"verse":11}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Th:3:8","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"we did not eat "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 10:25","book":"1Co","chapter":10,"verse":25,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" anyone’s food free of charge; "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Th 2:7","book":"1Th","chapter":2,"verse":7,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" instead, we labored "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rv 14:13","book":"Rev","chapter":14,"verse":13,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" and toiled, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Co 11:27","book":"2Co","chapter":11,"verse":27,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Th 2:9","book":"1Th","chapter":2,"verse":9,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"text","text":" working "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 18:3","book":"Act","chapter":18,"verse":3,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Eph 4:28","book":"Eph","chapter":4,"verse":28,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Jn 8","book":"2Jn","chapter":1,"verse":8,"letter":"h"},{"kind":"text","text":" night and day, so that we would not be a burden "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Co 2:5","book":"2Co","chapter":2,"verse":5,"letter":"i"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Th 2:9","book":"1Th","chapter":2,"verse":9,"letter":"j"},{"kind":"text","text":" to any of you. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"1Co 10:25","book":"1Co","chapter":10,"verse":25},{"label":"1Th 2:7","book":"1Th","chapter":2,"verse":7},{"label":"Rv 14:13","book":"Rev","chapter":14,"verse":13},{"label":"2Co 11:27","book":"2Co","chapter":11,"verse":27},{"label":"1Th 2:9","book":"1Th","chapter":2,"verse":9},{"label":"Ac 18:3","book":"Act","chapter":18,"verse":3},{"label":"Eph 4:28","book":"Eph","chapter":4,"verse":28},{"label":"2Jn 8","book":"2Jn","chapter":1,"verse":8},{"label":"2Co 2:5","book":"2Co","chapter":2,"verse":5},{"label":"1Th 2:9","book":"1Th","chapter":2,"verse":9}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Th:3:9","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"It is not that we don’t have the right "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mk 1:22","book":"Mrk","chapter":1,"verse":22,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 9:14","book":"Act","chapter":9,"verse":14,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 13:1","book":"Rom","chapter":13,"verse":1,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 9:4–14","book":"1Co","chapter":9,"verse":4,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" to support, but we did it to make ourselves an example to you so that you would imitate "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 8:5","book":"Heb","chapter":8,"verse":5,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"text","text":" us. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mk 1:22","book":"Mrk","chapter":1,"verse":22},{"label":"Ac 9:14","book":"Act","chapter":9,"verse":14},{"label":"Rm 13:1","book":"Rom","chapter":13,"verse":1},{"label":"1Co 9:4–14","book":"1Co","chapter":9,"verse":4},{"label":"Heb 8:5","book":"Heb","chapter":8,"verse":5}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Th:3:10","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"In fact, when we were with you, this is what we commanded you: “If anyone isn’t willing to work, he should not eat.” "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Th 4:11","book":"1Th","chapter":4,"verse":11,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"1Th 4:11","book":"1Th","chapter":4,"verse":11}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Th:3:11","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"For we hear that there are some among you who are idle. They are not busy but busybodies. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Tm 5:13","book":"1Ti","chapter":5,"verse":13,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"1Tm 5:13","book":"1Ti","chapter":5,"verse":13}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Th:3:12","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Now we command and exhort such people by the Lord Jesus Christ to work quietly and provide for themselves. "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":2,"text":"Lit they may eat their own bread"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[{"marker":2,"text":"Lit they may eat their own bread"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Th:3:13","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"But as for you, brothers and sisters, do not grow weary "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 18:1","book":"Luk","chapter":18,"verse":1,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Co 4:1","book":"2Co","chapter":4,"verse":1,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Co 4:16","book":"2Co","chapter":4,"verse":16,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gl 6:9","book":"Gal","chapter":6,"verse":9,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Eph 3:13","book":"Eph","chapter":3,"verse":13,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"text","text":" in doing good."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Lk 18:1","book":"Luk","chapter":18,"verse":1},{"label":"2Co 4:1","book":"2Co","chapter":4,"verse":1},{"label":"2Co 4:16","book":"2Co","chapter":4,"verse":16},{"label":"Gl 6:9","book":"Gal","chapter":6,"verse":9},{"label":"Eph 3:13","book":"Eph","chapter":3,"verse":13}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Th:3:14","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"If anyone does not obey our instruction in this letter, take note of that person; don’t associate with him, so that he may be ashamed. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Th:3:15","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Yet don’t consider him as an enemy, but warn him as a brother."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Th:3:16","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"May the Lord of peace "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Th 5:23","book":"1Th","chapter":5,"verse":23,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" himself give you peace always in every way. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Nm 6:26","book":"Num","chapter":6,"verse":26,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Eph 6:23","book":"Eph","chapter":6,"verse":23,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" The Lord be with all of you. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 15:33","book":"Rom","chapter":15,"verse":33,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 16:24","book":"1Co","chapter":16,"verse":24,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Co 13:13","book":"2Co","chapter":13,"verse":13,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ti 3:15","book":"Tit","chapter":3,"verse":15,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 13:25","book":"Heb","chapter":13,"verse":25,"letter":"h"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"1Th 5:23","book":"1Th","chapter":5,"verse":23},{"label":"Nm 6:26","book":"Num","chapter":6,"verse":26},{"label":"Eph 6:23","book":"Eph","chapter":6,"verse":23},{"label":"Rm 15:33","book":"Rom","chapter":15,"verse":33},{"label":"1Co 16:24","book":"1Co","chapter":16,"verse":24},{"label":"2Co 13:13","book":"2Co","chapter":13,"verse":13},{"label":"Ti 3:15","book":"Tit","chapter":3,"verse":15},{"label":"Heb 13:25","book":"Heb","chapter":13,"verse":25}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Th:3:17","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"I, Paul, am writing this greeting with my own hand, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 16:21","book":"1Co","chapter":16,"verse":21,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" which is an authenticating mark in every letter; this is how I write. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"1Co 16:21","book":"1Co","chapter":16,"verse":21}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Th:3:18","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"The grace of our Lord Jesus Christ be with you all."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]}]},"cachedAt":1783099552511}